pinballux (0.2.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix DMD auto-position values being overwritten by screen selection changes
  * Fix screen combo initialization selecting wrong screen on load
  * Preserve auto-positioned DMD coordinates when saving configuration

 -- Keith Phillips <keith@example.com>  Thu, 09 Oct 2025 15:00:00 -0500

pinballux (0.2.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix FullDMD displaying on playfield instead of dedicated DMD screen
  * Fix auto-positioned DMD settings being lost when reopening setup
  * Fix plunger button not working due to incorrect SDL mapping
  * Fix screen detection with non-sequential screen numbering
  * Fix ScreenRes.txt writing to wrong directory
  * Fix display position overrides not being saved/loaded
  * Add B2SDMD config writing for B2S Server compatibility
  * Add duplicate button mapping detection with warnings

 -- Keith Phillips <keith@example.com>  Wed, 08 Oct 2025 21:00:00 -0500

pinballux (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add automatic joystick GUID normalization for VPinball compatibility
  * Add DMD auto-positioning with one-click centering and sizing
  * Improved joystick configuration with SDL gamepad mapping
  * Resolution-aware DMD scaling for cabinet displays
  * Multi-monitor DMD positioning support

 -- Keith Phillips <keith@example.com>  Tue, 07 Oct 2025 12:30:00 -0500

pinballux (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Multi-monitor support for pinball cabinet displays
  * VPX table management and launching
  * Media integration with video, image, and audio support
  * Keyboard and joystick input handling
  * FTP media downloads from gameex.com
  * Setup GUI for configuration
  * Table Manager for media management
  * Automated VPinball download and installation

